<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>출석 관리 | 주차 선택</title>

    <link rel="stylesheet" 
          href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/orioncactus/pretendard@v1.3.8/dist/web/static/pretendard.css"/>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet"
          href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">

    <style>
        body { font-family: Pretendard, sans-serif; background:#F5F7FA; }

        .week-card {
            background: white;
            border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;
            border-radius: 14px;
            height: 8rem; /* h-32 */
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #374151;
            transition: 0.25s;
        }
        .week-card:hover {
            background: #EFF6FF;
            border-color: #3B82F6;
            color: #1D4ED8;
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0px 3px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
        }
        .week-card i {
            font-size: 26px;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body class="text-gray-800">

    {{> profLayout/profHeader }}

    <main class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 py-10">

        <div class="mb-8">
            <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 flex items-center gap-2">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-calendar-check text-blue-600"></i>
                출석 관리 – 주차 선택
            </h1>
            <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm mt-1">원하는 주차를 선택하여 출석을 관리하세요.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- 가로 넓게 3개씩 배치 -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6 mb-6">

            {{#weekList}}
                <a href="/courseAttendList?courseNo={{courseNo}}&weekNo={{.}}" class="week-card">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-calendar-week"></i>
                    {{.}}주차
                </a>
            {{/weekList}}

            {{^weekList}}
                <div class="col-span-4 text-center py-10 bg-white border rounded-lg text-gray-500">
                    등록된 주차가 없습니다.
                </div>
            {{/weekList}}

        </div>

    </main>

    {{> profLayout/profFooter }}

</body>
</html>
